nodes.text: Tobin Gantor was a male Human scientist. In 18 BBY, Gantor and his assistant Linna Naltree helped Jedi Master Ry-Gaul to hide from Imperial forces when Emperor Palpatine issued Order 66. Tobin had earlier married Linna. After rescuing her from Jenna Zan Arbor, the two moved to a new world, along with a new life.
